{{Top|leg}}
A '''Rylith power cell''' contained a [[rylith crystal]] that collected and stored solar energy. This feature allowed for the cell to be a popular choice in the design of many advanced weapon power supplies; the energy output of [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]], [[Blaster rifle/Legends|blaster rifles]], and [[Bowcaster/Legends|bowcasters]] was greatly increased. This type of power cell came in a range of energy output capability: basic, standard, advanced, superior, and pure.

